===Verb===
'''réussir'''
# (''intransitive'')to succeed
# (''intransitive'')to pass (a test)
#:''J'ai '''réussi''' à tous mes examens'''

====Usage note====
This verb is followed by [[à]] to make it into a [[transitive]] verb

